My Contribution

My primary responsibilities included:

* Analysis of NASA Kepler datasets
* Data cleaning and preprocessing
* Integration of multiple datasets with inconsistent structures
* Feature selection based on astrophysical principles
* Machine learning model development
* Presentation and technical explanation of the solution

One of the major challenges was combining several datasets that contained different structures and identifiers. By identifying common patterns and relationships between the datasets, it became possible to build a unified dataset suitable for machine learning.

Future Improvements

* Improved model accuracy
* Support for additional NASA datasets
* Advanced visualization of transit curves
* Habitability scoring system
* Public cloud deployment

Installation

Backend

cd backend
pip install -r requirements.txt
uvicorn app.main:app --reload

Frontend

cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev

